docker ps (list running containers)

docker run (start container with a command)

docker stop *container id* (stops the container)

docker start *container id* (starts the container)

docker ps -a (lists running and stopped containers)

docker run *container name and* *version* (pulls image and run container)

docker pull (pulls the image from repo to local computer)

docker run -d (run docker in detached mode)

docker run -d -p *port host*:*port of container*  (bind port of host to container)

docker logs *container id* (to get the logs)

docker run -d -p port host:port of container - -name (to rename a container)

docker network ls (list all the network)

docker network create name of network (creating a network)

docker images (list all the docker images)

docker rmi *image id* (delete a docker image)

docker rm *container id* (delete the container)
